THROUGHOUT MESSURMENT USING IPERF

iperf3 -s
iperf3 -c <server-ip>
iperf3 -c <server-ip> -R
iperf3 -c <server-ip> -t 20
iperf3 -c <server-ip> -P 5
iperf3 -c <server-ip> -u -b 100M
iperf3 -c <server-ip> --bidir
iperf3 -v

THROUGHPUT USING TC

sudo tc qdisc add dev enp3so root tbf rate 2mbit burst 32kbit latency 400ms
(bandwidth limit)

sudo tc qdisc add dev enp3so root netem loss 5%
(packet loss)

sudo tc qdisc add dev enp3so root netem delay 100ms 20ms distribution normal iperf3 -c 127.0.0.1
(jitter delay )


